h its Snapdragon X laptops is turning them into Copilot+ machines. These are special devices that can run Copilot AI tasks locally, so if you\u0026#39;re into using Microsoft\u0026#39;s assistant to help get things done, Copilot+ is perfect. However, even if you never touch the Copilot features, the Surface Laptop 2024 is still an excellent purchase; the hardware alone makes it worth your money.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003cp\u003eWith $481 taken off of the asking price, now is a great time to make the upgrade to a Surface Laptop. Just be sure to snag it before July 11th, when it\u0026#39;ll return to its regular price.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003c/div\u003e\n    \n                \n        \n        \n\n\n        \n\n\n\n\n\n                                            \n\n\n\n\n        \n    \u003c/article\u003e\n\n    \n            \n        \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
